OL,3,CFunding for Plaid Cymru's childcare
OL,4,Cpromises called into question
OL,6,FParents have told ITV News they
OL,7,Fbelieve the Welsh Government's
OL,8,Fproposed childcare plans are "too good
OL,9,Fto be true".
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru had pledged to expand free
OL,12,Fchildcare to 20 hours a week for 48
OL,13,Fweeks per year for children from nine
OL,14,Fmonths to four years old during their
OL,15,F2026 election campaign.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
