OL,3,CFunding for Plaid Cymru's childcare
OL,4,Cpromises called into question
OL,6,FDan Thomas, the leader of Reform
OL,7,FWales, called on the Welsh Government
OL,8,Fto share more details about the policy
OL,9,Fon Wednesday 10th June, saying it was
OL,10,Fessential for "transparency and
OL,11,Faccountability".
OL,13,FThe childcare pledge is estimated to
OL,14,Fcost #400 million annually, whilst the
OL,15,FInstitute for Fiscal Studies (IFS) has
OL,16,Fpreviously warned this could lead to
OL,17,Fcutbacks to other services or
OL,18,Fincreases in taxation.
OL,26,@rD@OOUsD@OO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
