OL,3,CFunding for Plaid Cymru's childcare
OL,4,Cpromises called into question
OL,6,FOne mother from the Caerleon Childcare
OL,7,Fgroup said she does not believe the
OL,8,Fgovernment will implement free
OL,9,Fchildcare provisions, saying "there
OL,10,Fmust be a catch somewhere."
OL,12,FShe said: "I used to work full time,
OL,13,Fnow I have to work three days a week,
OL,14,Fbecause I have to work to pay for
OL,15,Ftheir nursery."
OL,17,FAnother parent told ITV News, "I just
OL,18,Ffeel that if you do go back to work,
OL,19,Fby the time you pay out for your
OL,20,Fchildcare, you're not better off so
OL,21,Fyou might as well stay home.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1781125879
OL,3,CFunding for Plaid Cymru's childcare
OL,4,Cpromises called into question
OL,6,F"I just think that until it's actually
OL,7,Fconcrete that it's happening, then we
OL,8,Fwill believe when we see it."
OL,10,FSioned Williams, the Deputy First
OL,11,FMinister, said families in Wales had
OL,12,Fbeen "let down" by the previous
OL,13,Fgovernment and stressed Plaid Cymru is
OL,14,F"determined to change that".
OL,16,FShe said: "What we are saying is we
OL,17,Fneed a plan, we are having experts to
OL,18,Fhelp us phase this, but we know what
OL,19,Fthe initial phase looks like.
OL,26,@tD@FOUtD@OO]vD@AOUvD@[O]xD@KOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,462,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1781125879
OL,3,CFunding for Plaid Cymru's childcare
OL,4,Cpromises called into question
OL,6,F"The approach we are taking is one
OL,7,Fthat is evidence-based and expert-led,
OL,8,Fit is being guided by our new expert
OL,9,Fsteering group, exactly as we set out
OL,10,F(before the election)."
OL,12,F"As a Government, we are really
OL,13,Fcommitted to providing an update on
OL,14,Fthose initial costings and that phased
OL,15,Frollout of universal childcare," she
OL,16,Fadded.
OL,18,F"We are fixing the failures of the
OL,19,Fprevious government...we didn't see
OL,20,Ffocus, we didn't see funding, we
OL,21,Fdidn't see enough progress.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]tD@AOUwD@`O]zD@AOU
